  "body": "When I run remix-tests , out of memory happens, I have set \"NODE_OPTIONS=--max_old_space_size=10240\"\r\n\r\nAnd in remix web client often crash too. My contract a little complicated, code more than 1200 lines \r\n\r\nremix-tests -c 0.6.9 -v 5 tests/unit/A_test.sol\r\n\r\n\tüëÅ\t:: Running remix-tests - Unit testing for solidity ::\tüëÅ\r\n\r\n[14:33:32] info: verbosity level set to silly\r\n[14:33:32] info: Compiler version set to 0.6.9. Latest version is 0.8.14\r\nLoading remote solc version v0.6.9+commit.3e3065ac ...\r\n'creation of library remix_tests.sol:Assert pending...'\r\n\r\n\t‚óº  A_test\r\n\t‚úì  Check input add\r\n\t‚úì  Check input add2\r\n\t‚úì  Check input add3\r\n\r\n<--- Last few GCs --->\r\n\r\n[92306:0x130008000]    58188 ms: Scavenge 10063.7 (10254.2) -> 10062.8 (10275.2) MB, 26.7 / 0.0 ms  (average mu = 0.643, current mu = 0.496) allocation failure\r\n[92306:0x130008000]    63108 ms: Mark-sweep 10077.1 (10275.2) -> 10071.8 (10290.7) MB, 4915.4 / 0.0 ms  (average mu = 0.395, current mu = 0.029) allocation failure scavenge might not succeed\r\n\r\n\r\n<--- JS stacktrace --->\r\n\r\nFATAL ERROR: Reached heap limit Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory\r\n 1: 0x1004082dc node::Abort() [/Users/wxlo/.nvm/versions/node/v16.15.1/bin/node]\r\n 2: 0x100408464 node::errors::TryCatchScope::~TryCatchScope() [/Users/wxlo/.nvm/versions/node/v16.15.1/bin/node]\r\n 3: 0x100557b90 v8::Utils::ReportOOMFailure(v8::internal::Isolate*, char const*, bool) [/Users/wxlo/.nvm/versions/node/v16.15.1/bin/node]\r\n 4: 0x100557b24 v8::internal::V8::FatalProcessOutOfMemory(v8::internal::Isolate*, char const*, bool) [/Users/wxlo/.nvm/versions/node/v16.15.1/bin/node]\r\n 5: 0x1006db23c v8::internal::Heap::GarbageCollectionReasonToString(v8::internal::GarbageCollectionReason) [/Users/wxlo/.nvm/versions/node/v16.15.1/bin/node]\r\n 6: 0x1006d9d5c v8::internal::Heap::CollectGarbage(v8::internal::AllocationSpace, v8::internal::GarbageCollectionReason, v8::